Dambisa F. Moyo



Dr. Dambisa F. Moyo is Chief Executive Officer at Mildstorm LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Chevron Corp., Seagate Technology Plc, Seagate Technology LLC, Barrick Gold Corp., Barclays Plc and Barclays Bank Plc. Dr. Moyo was previously employed as Independent Non-Executive Director by SABMiller Ltd., a Principal by The World Bank, and Global Economist by Goldman Sachs International. He also served on the board at Lundin Petroleum AB and Room To Read. He received his undergraduate degree from American University, a graduate degree from Harvard Kennedy School of Government, an MBA from American University and a doctorate degree from the University of Oxford.



